IfLoop version 0.01
===================

IfLoop --- Add loop constructs to the if-elsif-else chain.

IfLoop allows the syntax 
if( A )
{
    do
    {
      #statements...
    }while( A )
}
else
{
    #default statments...
}

to be replaced by 

ifwhile(A)
{
    #statments...
}
else
{
    #default statements...
}

This condensed syntax is extendible just like the normal if-elsif-else
syntax.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

1) Filter::Util::Call
2) Text::Balanced 


